Interface GamePhysics

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PhysicsNode

    public interface GamePhysics
extends PhysicsNode
    Extends the PhysicsNode interface to provide a framework for more complex physics calculations suitable for game programming.

    This interface is subject to change! The Snapdragon2D Physics API is still under development.
